description.narrative: Evidence for improving programmes and policies on nutrition of newborns, children and women is made available; technical support in development of new law and revision of national standards is provided. Vaccine procurement capacity of Government is strengthened and pre-validation of elimination of mother-to-child transmission (eMTCT) of HIV and syphilis is in progress. | Status:On-track | As-of Date:31/12/2019
